    "It employs small grids, filters, or kernels to detect specific patterns such as lines, curves, or shapes within the receptive field.",
    "This multi-layered architecture of convolutional layers progressively interprets the visual information embedded in raw image data.",
    "To detect complex patterns and objects, each successive layer extracts feature maps that inform the deeper layers of the network.",
    "Pooling layers generate summary statistics for adjacent layers by downsampling data while retaining essential information.",
    "This process enhances object detection capabilities by providing invariance to rotations and translations."
